videos.description: Georgia Tech's Jordan Mason leaps over the Bowling Green defense for a 9-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech strikes with first TD of game

videos.description: Jarret Doege finds Deric Phouthavong in the end zone for a 30-yard Bowling Green touchdown.
videos.headline: Bowling Green closes the gap with 30-yard TD

videos.description: TaQuon Marshall slides into the end zone for a 2-yard Georgia Tech touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech continues to cruise with 2-yard TD

videos.description: Jordan Mason runs untouched into the end zone for a 33-yard Georgia Tech touchdown.
videos.headline: Georgia Tech's Mason runs for 33-yard TD

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Tobias Oliver sprints into the end zone for a 34-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Oliver continues to add to Georgia Tech's lead

videos.description: Georgia Tech's Anree Saint-Amour increases the lead with a 3-yard interception return touchdown.
videos.headline: Saint-Amour scores on pick-six for Georgia Tech
